                "value": "This character\u2019s arms shake lifting a sack of grain, and a stiff breeze feels like a shove. They tire after a short walk, leaning on fences to catch their breath. Village chores like chopping wood are a distant dream\u2014they\u2019d snap before the log does. Vigor is not their companion.",
